al.md                        # AR-036: Dify plugin integration proposal\n├── python-sdk/                        # **THE PYTHON SDK** (agentcube-sdk)\n├── sandbox-orchestration/             # design.md + spec.md\n├── session-routing/                   # design.md + spec.md\n├── session-store/                     # design.md + spec.md\n├── tasks.md                           # AR-023: CLI invoke/status commands tasks\n├── test/                              # Go test scripts\n├── test_spec.md                       # TDD specification (6 test case groups)\n└── testing/                           # Testing directory\n```\n\n**Note:** There is NO `sdk-python/` directory. The Python SDK lives at `python-sdk/`.\n\n---\n\n### 2. `python-sdk/` Directory Contents\n\nFull path: `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/python-sdk/`\n\n```\npython-sdk/\n├── .coverage                          # Coverage data\n├── .pytest_cache/                     # Pytest cache\n├── agentcube_sdk.egg-info/            # Installed package metadata\n│   ├── SOURCES.txt\n│   ├── PKG-INFO\n│   ├── requires.txt\n│   ├── dependency_links.txt\n│   └── top_level.txt\n├── agentcube/                         # SDK source package\n│   ├── __init__.py\n│   ├── agent_runtime.py\n│   ├── code_interpreter.py\n│   ├── exceptions.py\n│   ├── clients/\n│   │   ├── __init__.py\n│   │   ├── control_plane.py\n│   │   ├── code_interpreter_data_plane.py\n│   │   └── agent_runtime_data_plane.py\n│   └── utils/\n│       ├── __init__.py                # Empty\n│       ├── http.py\n│       ├── log.py\n│       └── utils.py\n├── design.md                          # AR-040: SDK test design document\n├── pyproject.toml                     # Package build config\n└── tests/                             # Test suite\n```\n\n---\n\n### 3. `tests/` Directory Contents\n\nFull path: `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/python-sdk/tests/`\n\n| File | Lines | Description |\n|------|-------|-------------|\n| `__init__.py` | 0 | Package marker (empty) |\n| `conftest.py` | 14 | Shared pytest fixtures (`mock_requests_session`, `mock_create_session`) |\n| `test_agent_runtime.py` | 837 | Tests for `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient` + `AgentRuntimeClient` (T-1 through T-10) |\n| `test_code_interpreter.py` | 635 | Tests for `CodeInterpreterClient` (T-1 through T-8) |\n| `test_control_plane.py` | 370 | Tests for `ControlPlaneClient` (T-1 through T-5) |\n| `test_data_plane.py` | 641 | Tests for `CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient` (T-1 through T-9) |\n| `test_exceptions.py` | 77 | Tests for exception hierarchy |\n| `test_imports.py` | 55 | Tests for package imports and `__all__` exports |\n| `test_utils.py` | 93 | Tests for `create_session`, `read_token_from_file`, `get_logger` |\n\n**Also present:** `__pycache__/` with compiled `.pyc` files for all test modules.\n\n---\n\n### 4. Test Infrastructure (conftest.py, pytest configs)\n\n**`conftest.py`** (14 lines):\n```python\nimport pytest\n\n@pytest.fixture\ndef mock_requests_session(mocker):\n    \"\"\"Mock requests.Session to avoid real HTTP calls.\"\"\"\n    mock_session = mocker.patch(\"requests.Session\")\n    return mock_session\n\n@pytest.fixture\ndef mock_create_session(mocker):\n    \"\"\"Mock the create_session utility.\"\"\"\n    return mocker.patch(\"agentcube.utils.http.create_session\")\n```\n\n**pytest configuration:** There is NO `pytest.ini`, `.pytest.ini`, `tox.ini`, or `pyproject.toml` `[tool.pytest]` section. Tests are run with:\n```bash\ncd python-sdk && python -m pytest tests/ -v\n```\n\n**Known bug in existing tests** (documented in `design.md`): Three methods in `test_code_interpreter.py` class `TestStop` are missing the `test_` prefix and will NOT be discovered by pytest:\n- `stop_closes_dp_client` (should be `test_stop_closes_dp_client`)\n- `stop_deletes_session` (should be `test_stop_deletes_session`)\n- `stop_closes_cp_client` (should be `test_stop_closes_cp_client`)\n\n---\n\n### 5. SDK Public API -- Complete Class/Function/Method Inventory\n\n#### Top-level exports (`agentcube/__init__.py`):\n- `CodeInterpreterClient`\n- `AgentRuntimeClient`\n\n#### Client exports (`agentcube/clients/__init__.py`):\n- `ControlPlaneClient`\n- `CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient`\n- `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient`\n\n#### `CodeInterpreterClient` (`agentcube/code_interpreter.py`, 161 lines):\n| Method | Signature |\n|--------|-----------|\n| `__init__` | `(name=\"my-interpreter\", namespace=\"default\", ttl=3600, workload_manager_url=None, router_url=None, auth_token=None, verbose=False, session_id=None)` |\n| `_init_data_plane` | `() -> None` |\n| `__enter__` | `() -> self` |\n| `__exit__` | `(exc_type, exc_val, exc_tb) -> None` |\n| `stop` | `() -> None` |\n| `execute_command` | `(command: str, timeout: Optional[float]=None) -> str` |\n| `run_code` | `(language: str, code: str, timeout: Optional[float]=None) -> str` |\n| `write_file` | `(content: str, remote_path: str) -> None` |\n| `upload_file` | `(local_path: str, remote_path: str) -> None` |\n| `download_file` | `(remote_path: str, local_path: str) -> None` |\n| `list_files` | `(path: str=\".\") -> Any` |\n\n#### `AgentRuntimeClient` (`agentcube/agent_runtime.py`, 79 lines):\n| Method | Signature |\n|--------|-----------|\n| `__init__` | `(agent_name: str, namespace=\"default\", router_url=None, verbose=False, session_id=None, timeout=120, connect_timeout=5.0)` |\n| `__enter__` | `() -> self` |\n| `__exit__` | `(exc_type, exc_val, exc_tb) -> None` |\n| `invoke` | `(payload: Dict[str, Any], timeout: Optional[float]=None) -> Any` |\n| `close` | `() -> None` |\n\n#### `ControlPlaneClient` (`agentcube/clients/control_plane.py`, 96 lines):\n| Method | Signature |\n|--------|-----------|\n| `__init__` | `(workload_manager_url=None, auth_token=None, timeout=120, connect_timeout=5.0, pool_connections=10, pool_maxsize=10)` |\n| `create_session` | `(name=\"my-interpreter\", namespace=\"default\", metadata=None, ttl=3600) -> str` |\n| `delete_session` | `(session_id: str) -> bool` |\n| `close` | `() -> None` |\n\n#### `CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient` (`agentcube/clients/code_interpreter_data_plane.py`, 176 lines):\n| Method | Signature |\n|--------|-----------|\n| `__init__` | `(session_id, router_url=None, namespace=None, cr_name=None, base_url=None, timeout=120, connect_timeout=5.0, pool_connections=10, pool_maxsize=10)` |\n| `_request` | `(method, endpoint, body=None, **kwargs) -> Response` |\n| `execute_command` | `(command: Union[str, List[str]], timeout=None) -> str` |\n| `run_code` | `(language, code, timeout=None) -> str` |\n| `write_file` | `(content, remote_path) -> None` |\n| `upload_file` | `(local_path, remote_path) -> None` |\n| `download_file` | `(remote_path, local_path) -> None` |\n| `list_files` | `(path=\".\") -> Any` |\n| `close` | `() -> None` |\n\n#### `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient` (`agentcube/clients/agent_runtime_data_plane.py`, 80 lines):\n| Method | Signature |\n|--------|-----------|\n| `__init__` | `(router_url, namespace, agent_name, timeout=120, connect_timeout=5.0, pool_connections=10, pool_maxsize=10)` |\n| `bootstrap_session_id` | `() -> str` |\n| `invoke` | `(session_id, payload: Dict, timeout=None) -> Response` |\n| `close` | `() -> None` |\n| Class constant | `SESSION_HEADER = \"x-agentcube-session-id\"` |\n\n#### Exception hierarchy (`agentcube/exceptions.py`, 21 lines):\n- `AgentCubeError(Exception)` -- base\n- `CommandExecutionError(AgentCubeError)` -- has `exit_code`, `stderr`, `command` attributes\n- `SessionError(AgentCubeError)` -- docstring only, not raised by core\n- `DataPlaneError(AgentCubeError)` -- docstring only, not raised by core\n\n#### Utilities:\n- `create_session(pool_connections=10, pool_maxsize=10) -> requests.Session` (`utils/http.py`)\n- `read_token_from_file(file_path: str) -> str` (`utils/utils.py`)\n- `get_logger(name: str, level=INFO) -> logging.Logger` (`utils/log.py`)\n\n---\n