tRuntimeDataPlaneClient`).\n4. **Test suite has 7 test files + conftest.py**, totaling ~2,708 lines of test code.\n5. **Known bug**: 3 test methods in `test_code_interpreter.py` lack the `test_` prefix and are silently skipped by pytest.\n6. **No `test_integration.py` file exists** despite being planned in `design.md` section 5.3.\n7. **Dependencies**: `requests`, `PyJWT>=2.0.0`, `cryptography`. No dev dependencies declared in `pyproject.toml`.\n8. **The `SOURCES.txt` in egg-info** is out of date -- it lists only 4 test files but 7 exist.\n</task_result>","metadata":{"sessionId":"ses_284805416ffe9g5mfFMhPBQRRy","model":{"modelID":"qwen3.6-plus","providerID":"alibaba-cn"},"truncated":false},"title":"Explore agentcube project structure","time":{"start":1775893457895,"end":1775893763602}}}}
